---
title: PIP — Pallet ID Pull Flow
---
flowchart TD
    START([Worker opens PIP\nsrc/pages/PIPPage.tsx]) --> S1

    S1[State: selectFunction\nshow CA / CF / FP buttons]
    S1 --> SEL[Worker taps pull function\nhandleSelectFunction]
    SEL --> S2

    S2[State: ready\nlabelField auto-focuses\nvia useEffect on screenState]

    S2 --> SCAN_L{Scanner fires\nor numpad submit\nhandleLabelScan}

    SCAN_L --> API_L[GET /api/labels/:id\napi/functions/labels.ts — getLabel\nvalidate status\nresolve Label→Pallet→Location]

    API_L --> L_FOUND{Found?}
    L_FOUND -->|NOT_FOUND| ERR_L1[Error: Label not found\nlabelField cleared\nremain in ready]
    L_FOUND -->|BAD STATUS\ne.g. PULLED/CANCELLED| ERR_L2[Error: Invalid status\nlabelField cleared\nremain in ready]
    L_FOUND -->|OK| FN_CHECK{pullFunction\nmatch?}

    FN_CHECK -->|Mismatch| ERR_L3[Error: Wrong function\nlabelField cleared\nremain in ready]
    FN_CHECK -->|Match| S3

    ERR_L1 --> S2
    ERR_L2 --> S2
    ERR_L3 --> S2

    S3[State: verifying\nstores labelData\npidField auto-focuses\nvia useEffect on screenState]

    S3 --> RESCAN{New label\nscanned while verifying?}
    RESCAN -->|Yes — handleLabelScan\nissue #45: no status-bar\nupdate on a plain rescan| RELOAD[Clear PID + UPC + Location fields\nreload label data\nsilently]
    RELOAD --> S3

    S3 --> VER_PATH{Worker scans one of:}

    VER_PATH -->|Pallet ID\nPID field| PID_VERIFY[POST /api/pulls/verify\nwith palletId\napi/functions/pulls.ts — verifyPull]
    VER_PATH -->|UPC\nUPC field — issue #82| UPC_VERIFY[POST /api/pulls/verify\nwith upc\napi/functions/pulls.ts — verifyPull]
    VER_PATH -->|Location\nLocationEntryFields 3-box| LOC_VERIFY[POST /api/pulls/verify\nwith location + wasScanned\napi/functions/pulls.ts — verifyPull]

    PID_VERIFY --> PID_OK{Result?}
    PID_OK -->|PALLET_MISMATCH| ERR_PID[Error: Incorrect Pallet ID\npidField cleared + re-focused]
    PID_OK -->|WRONG_PULL_FUNCTION| ERR_PID2[Error: Pull function mismatch]
    PID_OK -->|OK| SUCCESS

    UPC_VERIFY --> UPC_OK{UPC match\nagainst pallet's DPCI?}
    UPC_OK -->|No — ALTERNATE_MISMATCH| ERR_UPC[Error: Invalid UPC\nupcField cleared + re-focused]
    UPC_OK -->|Yes| SUCCESS

    LOC_VERIFY --> LOC_BIN{aisle+bin match?}
    LOC_BIN -->|No — ALTERNATE_MISMATCH, any\nfunction/entry method| ERR_LOC[Error: Invalid Location\nLocationEntryFields cleared + re-focused]
    LOC_BIN -->|Yes| LOC_METHOD{wasScanned?}
    LOC_METHOD -->|No — hand-entered\nany pullFunction| LOC_LEVEL_MANUAL{level also\nmatches?}
    LOC_LEVEL_MANUAL -->|Yes| SUCCESS
    LOC_LEVEL_MANUAL -->|No — full match required,\nno recovery popup| ERR_LOC
    LOC_METHOD -->|Yes — scanned| LOC_FN{pullFunction?}
    LOC_FN -->|CF\nlevel ignored| SUCCESS
    LOC_FN -->|CA| LOC_LEVEL_CA{level also\nmatches?}
    LOC_LEVEL_CA -->|Yes| SUCCESS
    LOC_LEVEL_CA -->|No — full match required,\nno recovery popup| ERR_LOC
    LOC_FN -->|FP| LOC_LEVEL{level also\nmatches?}
    LOC_LEVEL -->|Yes| SUCCESS
    LOC_LEVEL -->|No — issues #48/#49\nLEVEL_MISMATCH 400| CORRECT[LevelCorrectionDialog — issue #72:\nWhat level was this pallet\nactually pulled from?\nworker types the level]
    CORRECT -->|Cancel — cancelLevelMismatch\ntreated as Invalid Location| ERR_LOC
    CORRECT -->|Confirm Level —\nresubmit corrected level +\nconfirmLevelMismatch: true| SUCCESS

    ERR_PID --> S3
    ERR_PID2 --> S3
    ERR_UPC --> S3
    ERR_LOC --> S3

    SUCCESS[onPullSuccess\nlabel marked PULLED\nquantities deducted\nwriteLog PULL]

    SUCCESS --> HIST[Append history entry\nlocation + updatedQty + timestamp]
    HIST --> MSG[MessageBar: success\nPull location + remaining qty]
    MSG --> RESET[Clear all fields\nsetLabelData null\nsetScreenState ready]
    RESET --> S2

    style START fill:#1a1a1a,stroke:#555,color:#fff
    style SUCCESS fill:#003300,stroke:#006600,color:#fff
    style ERR_L1 fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_L2 fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_L3 fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_PID fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_PID2 fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_UPC fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style ERR_LOC fill:#330000,stroke:#660000,color:#ff8080
    style CORRECT fill:#332200,stroke:#665500,color:#ffcc66
